            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "For quantum energies ranging from 0 to 0.25 MeV above",
                "threshold or 2.183-2.433 X-ray energy. With even less",
                "precision it is possible to estimate the order of",
                "magnitude of the total cross section: reasonable",
                "guesses as to the effective number of quanta and the",
                "sensitivity of neutron detection lead to a value of",
                "about 10**(-28) cm2."
